<paragraph id="09D888861C874AA35D5809C97206EF7E" pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="778079E37322638D4F991E78846F90B6" pageId="0" pageNumber="41">D. Probst collected a small rhizome segment at the second site that he grew but did not voucher. An image of the plant was obtained for documentation and deposited in UC. A specimen voucher will be made and also deposited at UC when the plant reflowers.</paragraph>
